Exercise 12.1: Applying Margin and Padding Utilities
Margin (m-3, mt-4), Padding (p-2, py-5) Usage Example:
<div class="container mt-4 p-3 border bg-light">
  <h2 class="mb-3">Welcome to Our Event Portal</h2>

  <section class="m-3 p-2 bg-white border">
    <h4>Upcoming Events</h4>
    <p class="py-5">
      Discover amazing events happening near you. This section has vertical padding (`py-5`) for better spacing.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-4 p-3 bg-white border">
    <h4>Register Now</h4>
    <p class="p-2">
      Fill out the registration form to secure your spot!
    </p>
  </section>
</div>

